Package: synopR
Title: Tidy Decoding of SYNOP Meteorological Messages
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ezequiel", "Elias", , "elezeru15@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A specialized tool for decoding raw WMO SYNOP messages into 
    tidy data frames. It supports batch processing of messages from the 
    same station, extracting data from Sections 0, 1, and 3, including 
    temperatures, pressure, wind, clouds, and precipitation.
